SBML2LaTeX version 0.9.9

Packages
org.sbml.tolatex This package contains parsers for MIRIAM and SBO files, helper classes for LaTeX code writing and GUI layout setup, string operations, an interface for general conversion of SBML into some human-readable report and the actual converter SBML2LaTeX.
org.sbml.tolatex.gui Some basic elements for a simple graphical user interface.
org.sbml.tolatex.io This package contains all necessary classes for writing LaTeX files and for parsing MIRIAM files.
org.sbml.tolatex.util Provides specialized helper classes for String operations on LaTeX source code.
